{"title_page": "List of programming broadcast by Colors Rishtey", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\nThis is a list of programming broadcast on each feed of [[Colors Rishtey]] around the world. It mainly broadcasts reruns of [[Colors TV|Colors]] series while also airing new series and shows from other networks.\n\n== Indian feed ==\nThese are the programs broadcast on the Indian feed of Rishtey. This feed broadcasts only in the [[Indian subcontinent]], which includes [[India]], [[Pakistan]], [[Bangladesh]], [[Sri Lanka]], [[Bhutan]], [[Maldives]], and [[Nepal]].\n\n=== Drama ===\n*''[[Laagi Tujhse Lagan]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/programmes/balika-vadhu/params/tvprogramme/programmeid-10000001406870000/channelid-10000000018500000/starttime-201802171600|title=Balika Vadhu TV Serial & New Episodes On Rishtey \u2013 Latest News, Photos & Videos|website=The Times of India|access-date=2018-02-17}}</ref>''\n*''[[Swaragini - Jodein Rishton Ke Sur|Swaragini]]''\n*''[[Sasural Simar Ka]]''\n*''[[Udaan (2014 TV series)|Udaan]]''\n\n=== Animated ===\n* ''[[Chhoti Anandi]]''\n* ''[[Dora the Explorer]]''\n* ''[[Gattu Battu]]''\n* ''[[Go, Diego, Go!]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/programmes/go,-diego,-go!/params/tvprogramme/programmeid-30000000549654482/channelid-10000000018500000/starttime-201802170800|title=Go, Diego, Go! TV Serial & New Episodes On Rishtey \u2013 Latest News, Photos & Videos|website=The Times of India|access-date=2018-02-17}}</ref>\n* ''[[Jungle Book]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/programmes/jungle-book/params/tvprogramme/programmeid-30000000549845969/channelid-10000000018500000/starttime-201802170830|title=Jungle Book TV Serial & New Episodes On Rishtey \u2013 Latest News, Photos & Videos|website=The Times of India|access-date=2018-02-17}}</ref>\n* ''[[Keymon Ache]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/programmes/keymon